{"tid":668862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳安全島慶回歸藝術品「令人不安」   發展局承諾兩個月內清拆","createTime":"2018-05-18T03:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T06:28:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6080989c30cfcca8827685617dc8ea5c79c8d25d","tid":668862,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"政府近日在葵芳一個安全島上安裝了一件慶回歸藝術品，但有街坊反映「令人不安」，發展局承諾區議員兩個月內清拆。 <br />\n<br />\n該件藝術品以磚頭堆砌成山形，擺放在葵涌廣場對開的安全島上，是慶回歸二十周年的藝術比賽得獎作品之一，簡介指設計概念是「使等待過馬路變成了愉快的經歷」，由設計、建造至清拆，共花公帑八十五萬元，原本計劃可以擺一年。當區區議員吳劍昇指，有居民反映似「山墳」，每次經過都感到不安及不吉利，亦對駕駛者不便。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他與發展局人員到現場視察，局方承諾兩個月內清拆。發展局就指藝術品經過專業評估，確保符合交通安全要求，會細心參考市民意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527250/即時新聞/當局將拆葵芳安全島慶回歸藝術品\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527250%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%86%E8%91%B5%E8%8A%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B3%B6%E6%85%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%93%81&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c6843af1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F527250%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%86%E8%91%B5%E8%8A%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B3%B6%E6%85%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%93%81&h=52e74242\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/527250/即時新聞/當局將拆葵芳安全島慶回歸藝術品</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/island2-01_FUnIT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fisland2-01_FUnIT_1200x0.png&h=1adc31f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc9a2dc7d92b920904fbb6b0631c3b8f5d353e87","tid":668862,"uid":87123,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"gdp<img src=\"/assets/fa